---
title: Spiced Chicken with Tahini-Yogurt Dressing
description: This delicious chicken recipe is an ode to the Middle East; a culinary playground full of sesame, citrus and spice! Perfectly cooked chicken doused in nutty tahini and a tahini-yogurt dressing is the stuff your dreams are made of.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spiced-chicken-81562500.jpg
